import React from 'react'
import './index.css'

export default function index() {
    return ( <
        div className = "footer" >
        <
        div className = "song" >
        <
        img src = "https://unsplash.it/200"
        alt = "album art"
        className = "sm-hide" / >
        <
        div className = "info" >
        <
        p className = "title" > Panda < /p> <
        p className = "artist" > Cattee < /p> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        div className = "controls" >
        <
        i className = "fa fa-step-backward" > < /i> <
        i className = "fa fa-pause" > < /i> <
        i className = "fa fa-step-forward" > < /i> <
        i className = "fa fa-repeat sm-hide" > < /i> <
        i className = "fa fa-like sm-hide" > < /i> <
        /div> <
        /div>
    )
}
